column2: Chewy, Inc. engages in the provision of pure-play e-commerce business. The company is headquartered in Dania Beach, Florida and currently employs 9,833 full-time employees. The Companyâ€™s brands include A Pet Hub, A&E Cage Company, ABO Gear, Acurel, Addiction, Advance, Advantage, Apocaps, Atopia, Audbudon Part and Ark Naturals. The firm's product offerings by categories include tablet, chewable tablet, solution, capsule, injectable, suspension and ointment. The firm offers over 1600 brands with its operation in 13 locations. The firm offers its products and services through its Website and mobile applications.
